net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.factory.mapper
Class AbstractResourceMapper

java.lang.Object
  net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.factory.mapper.AbstractResourceMapper
Direct Known Subclasses:
ResourceBundleDirMapper
public abstract class AbstractResourceMapper
extends java.lang.Object

Base class to implement map-based automatic bundles generators. The generated bundles are added to a Map instance in which the keys are bundles ids and the values are the bundles.

Author:
Jordi Hernández Sellés
